			<p class="reason-text">I developped Miner.cloud because I realized that most of my energy was spent on tools, and not ont learning Japanese.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<%= image_tag("profile-picture.png", :alt => "Lois Lin", :class => "profile-pic img-responsive") %>
